{"tid":2397961,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《鴨兔元旦》展覽永久終止！ Miffy官方：廣州美院教授自願交還版權","createTime":"2021-02-07T01:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T01:22:25.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b30ce2c147e4e3f356b4c98ab54e80c78562d6ee","tid":2397961,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T01:05:53.000Z","msg":"廣州美術學院教授馮峰創作的一款「鴨兔」卡通人物，被指與荷蘭畫家創作的經典卡通兔Ｍiffy極為相似。被指炒襲的馮峰還辯稱受到維特根斯坦（Ludwig Wittgenstein）的《哲學研究》的鴨兔圖形啟發，更揚言「人人都是藝術家」。今日，Miffy（內地稱米菲）官方發佈「米菲與《鴨兔元旦》聯合聲明」，各方同意永久停止在未來的展覽及商業活動中使用該受爭議的作品。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210206/NBGIXGRVH5CJDBS2WMOZUP7E4E/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210206%2FNBGIXGRVH5CJDBS2WMOZUP7E4E%2F&d=ZxGTC5m4wH5D2fXTYNKMIbTKTGNgLIIXgyzGYx6bzTs%3D&h=0be726b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210206%2FNBGIXGRVH5CJDBS2WMOZUP7E4E%2F&h=1f20b015\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210206/NBGIXGRVH5CJDBS2WMOZUP7E4E/</a>"},{"pid":"c635a5083b3b1384eed33a501c836edf43fe47d0","tid":2397961,"uid":335434,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T01:22:25.000Z","msg":"支国真係痴撚綫 喺外国咁樣抄樣咁出名嘅牌子賠錢都賠到你破產啦 喺支国竟然要被抄襲間公司配合抄人果個出聯合聲明當無數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}